<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"> <channel><title>13m0n4de&#39;s notebook</title><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/</link><atom:link href="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><docs>https://github.com/13m0n4de/notebook</docs><language>zh</language> <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 06:46:20 -0000</pubDate> <lastBuildDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 06:46:20 -0000</lastBuildDate> <ttl>1440</ttl> <generator>MkDocs RSS plugin - v1.17.0</generator> <image> <url>None</url> <title>13m0n4de's notebook</title><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/</link> </image> <item> <title>Malware Analysis: PowerGhost</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Malware Analysis: PowerGhost&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;近期应急响应事件中遇到的病毒样本，处置不复杂，但搜罗了一圈发现网上没有特别详尽的病毒分析。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;于是开了个新系列 Malware Analysis，我的第一篇病毒分析文章。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;病毒分析和应急响应处置在笔记中同步了一份：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../sec/malwares/powerghost.md&#34;&gt;Security::Malwares::PowerGhost&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../sec/incidents/powerghost.md&#34;&gt;Security::Incidents::PowerGhost&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/04/01/malware-analysis-powerghost.html</link> <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/04/01/malware-analysis-powerghost.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Keep It Simple, Security People</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Keep It Simple, Security People&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;如果你不知道的话，我建了个仓库 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/my-exploits&#34;&gt;13m0n4de/my-exploits&lt;/a&gt;，存放个人开发的各种漏洞利用脚本。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;只是平常要用，用得上就写，写了就完善一下传上去，...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/03/18/keep-it-simple-security-people.html</link> <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/03/18/keep-it-simple-security-people.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>CVE Roulette #1: pngcheck</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;CVE Roulette #1: pngcheck&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这是 CVE Roulette 系列的第一篇文章。抽到了 CVE-2020-27818，研究着研究着就顺手把 pngcheck 的历史漏洞都看了个遍 :)&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/01/30/cve-roulette-1-pngcheck.html</link> <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2025/01/30/cve-roulette-1-pngcheck.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Ricing My Arch Linux</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Ricing My Arch Linux&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;花了点时间从 i3 迁移到 Hyprland，终于把凌乱的 Dotfiles 整理好了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这次除了整理配置文件，还将整体配色方案从 Nord 切换到了 Catppuccin Macchiato，并且统一了包括网站在内的所有主题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dotfiles 仓库：&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/dotfiles&#34;&gt;github.com/13m0n4de/dotfiles&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/12/06/ricing-my-arch-linux.html</link> <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/12/06/ricing-my-arch-linux.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Coffee and Random Thoughts: Hackergame 2024 ☕</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Coffee and Random Thoughts: Hackergame 2024 ☕&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;猜猜是谁一周没出门阴暗地打 &lt;a href=&#34;https://hack.lug.ustc.edu.cn/&#34;&gt;Hackergame&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;今年的题目依旧有难度有意思，题解想写细致一点，加上最近事情很多，估计进度会很慢。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;题解仓库：&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/hackergame2024-writeups&#34;&gt;13m0n4de/hackergame2024-writeups&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/11/09/coffee-and-random-thoughts-hackergame-2024-.html</link> <pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/11/09/coffee-and-random-thoughts-hackergame-2024-.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>HackerRank in Racket: Part 3</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;HackerRank in Racket: Part 3&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这里是使用 Racket 完成 HackerRank 函数式编程题目的第三章，包含函数关系和几何计算（22 - 26 题）。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/16/hackerrank-in-racket-part-3.html</link> <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/16/hackerrank-in-racket-part-3.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>HackerRank in Racket: Part 2</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;HackerRank in Racket: Part 2&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这里是使用 Racket 完成 HackerRank 函数式编程题目的第二章，包含数学函数和 Lambda 演算（11 - 21 题）。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/13/hackerrank-in-racket-part-2.html</link> <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/13/hackerrank-in-racket-part-2.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>HackerRank in Racket: Part 1</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;HackerRank in Racket: Part 1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这里是使用 Racket 完成 HackerRank 函数式编程题目的第一章，包含基础函数和列表操作（0 - 10 题）。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/11/hackerrank-in-racket-part-1.html</link> <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/06/11/hackerrank-in-racket-part-1.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Wireworld Simulator Using the Raylib: Part2</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Wireworld Simulator Using the Raylib: Part2&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;继续&lt;a href=&#34;./wireworld_simulator_using_the_raylib_part1.md&#34;&gt;上一部分&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这部分主要实现 &lt;strong&gt;无限画布&lt;/strong&gt; 的功能，包含视角移动、视图缩放、网格自动拓展。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;项目地址：&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/wireworld&#34;&gt;github.com/13m0n4de/wireworld&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/23/wireworld-simulator-using-the-raylib-part2.html</link> <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/23/wireworld-simulator-using-the-raylib-part2.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Wireworld Simulator Using the Raylib: Part1</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Wireworld Simulator Using the Raylib: Part1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;用 Raylib 写个 Wireworld 模拟器，试试自己能不能用 C 语言顺畅地做游戏。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章是制作过程的详细记录，记录编码、设计的思路和步骤，标题会非常细碎。当作一个 Step by Step 教程也许可以，每个阶段都附了完整代码可以对照。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;项目地址：&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/wireworld&#34;&gt;github.com/13m0n4de/wireworld&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/20/wireworld-simulator-using-the-raylib-part1.html</link> <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/20/wireworld-simulator-using-the-raylib-part1.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Bad Apple!! on LemonCore</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Bad Apple!! on LemonCore&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;前段时间写了个操作系统，取名叫 LemonCore，惯例，播放一下 BadApple。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;OS：&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/13m0n4de/lemon-core&#34;&gt;github.com/13m0n4de/lemon-core&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;App: &lt;a href=&#34;https://gist.github.com/13m0n4de/238b13f361e0326a0e8868e00119fb2a&#34;&gt;gist.github.com/13m0n4de/238b13f361e0326a0e8868e00119fb2a&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Video: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm8628149&#34;&gt;[Touhou] Bad Apple!! PV [Shadow]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/12/bad-apple-on-lemoncore.html</link> <pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/05/12/bad-apple-on-lemoncore.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Search Engines in 2024: Will Spaces Still Matter?</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Search Engines in 2024: Will Spaces Still Matter?&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;小的时候，第一次学会上网搜索内容，人们告诉我：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;「把你的中文词语用空格分开」&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;我记到现在，甚至有点“强迫”。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/04/07/search-engines-in-2024-will-spaces-still-matter.html</link> <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/04/07/search-engines-in-2024-will-spaces-still-matter.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>I Need a Done List, Not a Todo List</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;I Need a Done List, Not a Todo List&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;笔记本有个 Todo List，记录着许多待办事项。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;然后它们就一直待办。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/25/i-need-a-done-list-not-a-todo-list.html</link> <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/25/i-need-a-done-list-not-a-todo-list.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Exploring the Hare Programming Language: Part 1</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Exploring the Hare Programming Language: Part 1&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇依旧是跟屁虫系列。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tsoding Daily 的新视频：&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2E3E_Rh3mvw&#34;&gt;Hare Programming Language&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;我决定先自己探索一遍再看。&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/18/exploring-the-hare-programming-language-part-1.html</link> <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/18/exploring-the-hare-programming-language-part-1.html</guid> </item> <item> <title>Including C File Over HTTPS</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Including C File Over HTTPS&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;实现了一个有意思的效果，让 C 语言可以从互联网上 &lt;code&gt;#!c #include&lt;/code&gt; 头文件。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;```c title=&#39;include_files_from_internet.c&#39;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1&gt;define STB_SPRINTF_IMPLEMENTATION&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;include &lt;a href=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nothings/stb/master/stb_sprintf.h&#34;&gt;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nothings/stb/master/stb_sprintf.h&lt;/a&gt; // &amp;lt;- look at this&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;include &lt;stdio.h&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;int main() { char buffer[20];&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;// Using functions defined by stb_sprintf.hstbsp_sprintf(buffer, &#34;Hello %s&#34;, &#34;NAVI&#34;);puts(buffer);return 0;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;}```&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;你知道的，4202 年，Everything Over HTTPS（笑）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;My TinyCC Patch: &lt;a href=&#34;https://gist.github.com/13m0n4de/84912522cce6db31da069baf1add04f8&#34;&gt;https://gist.github.com/13m0n4de/84912522cce6db31da069baf1add04f8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;My Chibicc Patch: &lt;a href=&#34;https://gist.github.com/13m0n4de/f2b4b8e71ce6a93530cbe9e4e45cbe71&#34;&gt;https://gist.github.com/13m0n4de/f2b4b8e71ce6a93530cbe9e4e45cbe71&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><link>https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/17/including-c-file-over-https.html</link> <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/feed_rss_created.xml">13m0n4de's notebook</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://13m0n4de.vercel.app/blog/2024/02/17/including-c-file-over-https.html</guid> </item> </channel></rss>